Sentencas: It is well known that hetero-interfaces in (La,Sr)CoO3/(La,Sr)(2)CoO4 (LSC113/214) are beneficial in catalyzing ORR for SOFC cathodes.
Titulo: One pot synthesis of (La,Sr)CoO3/(La,Sr)2CoO4 for IT-SOFCs cathodes

Sentencas: This can be achieved by synthesizing the individual phases and mixing them together.
Titulo: One pot synthesis of (La,Sr)CoO3/(La,Sr)2CoO4 for IT-SOFCs cathodes

Sentencas: In this study, so as to maximize the hetero interfaces, an alternative method was used in which one pot Pechini method was employed to synthesize a two-phase structure.
Titulo: One pot synthesis of (La,Sr)CoO3/(La,Sr)2CoO4 for IT-SOFCs cathodes

Sentencas: LSC113/214 two phase structures from one precursors solution were successfully synthesized without the formation of any undesired third phase for the first time.
Titulo: One pot synthesis of (La,Sr)CoO3/(La,Sr)2CoO4 for IT-SOFCs cathodes

Sentencas: It was found that a minimum temperature of 800 degrees C was necessary so as to obtain the fully crystallized dual phase powder.
Titulo: One pot synthesis of (La,Sr)CoO3/(La,Sr)2CoO4 for IT-SOFCs cathodes

Sentencas: Two phase structures of molar fractions from 0.40 to 0.60 was targeted and were successfully obtained with some deviations.
Titulo: One pot synthesis of (La,Sr)CoO3/(La,Sr)2CoO4 for IT-SOFCs cathodes

Sentencas: Impedance measurements were carried out on porous conventional symmetric cells fabricated with the synthesized dual phase powders between 400 and 700 degrees C.
Titulo: One pot synthesis of (La,Sr)CoO3/(La,Sr)2CoO4 for IT-SOFCs cathodes

Sentencas: The dual phase powders had improved electrode performance as compared to single phase and physically mixed powders, but this was limited down to 500 degrees C. (C) 2018
